<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>GreenNest - Plant Disease Detection</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .first-section {
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6)), url('/views/Images/EgyptianFarmer.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .hero-content {
            max-width: 900px;
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out;
        }

        .head-one-main {
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        .hero-subtitle {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .btn-join-us {
            background: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 1.2rem 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            display: inline-block;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-join-us:hover {
            background: #45a049;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.4);
        }

        .features-section {
            padding: 6rem 2rem;
            background: white;
        }

        .content-section-two {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .content-section-two h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            position: relative;
            padding-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .content-section-two h2::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 80px;
            height: 4px;
            background: #4CAF50;
            border-radius: 2px;
        }

        .features-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }

        .feature-card {
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #4CAF50;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .feature-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .feature-card p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .second-section {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8)), url('/views/Images/farmersImages.webp');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            background-attachment: fixed;
            padding: 6rem 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        .cta-content {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .cta-content h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .cta-content p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .icons {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 4rem;
        }

        .icons span {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            color: #4CAF50;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .icons span:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1);
            color: #45a049;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .head-one-main {
                font-size: 2.2rem;
            }
            .hero-subtitle {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
            }
            .content-section-two h2 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            .features-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            .feature-card {
                padding: 1.5rem;
            }
            .cta-content h2 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            .icons {
                gap: 2.5rem;
            }
            .icons span {
                font-size: 2.8rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <section class="first-section">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1 class="head-one-main">Discover, Nurture, and Protect Your Plants with AI-Powered Care</h1>
            <p class="hero-subtitle">Join thousands of farmers using advanced technology to ensure healthier crops</p>
            <a href="/account" class="btn-join-us">Get Started Now</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features-section">
        <div class="content-section-two">
            <h2>Empowering Agriculture with AI</h2>
            <div class="features-grid">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-leaf feature-icon"></i>
                    <h3>Smart Detection</h3>
                    <p>Instant plant disease detection using advanced AI technology</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-chart-line feature-icon"></i>
                    <h3>Real-time Analysis</h3>
                    <p>Get immediate insights and treatment recommendations</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt feature-icon"></i>
                    <h3>Mobile Access</h3>
                    <p>Monitor your plants' health anytime, anywhere</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="second-section">
        <div class="cta-content">
            <h2>Join the Future of Farming</h2>
            <p>Experience the power of AI-driven plant care technology. Upload a photo, get instant analysis, and protect your crops effectively.</p>
            <div class="icons">
                <span><i class="fas fa-camera"></i></span>
                <span><i class="fas fa-mobile-screen-button"></i></span>
                <span><i class="fas fa-seedling"></i></span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
</body>
</html>